ily:宋体;\">开卷</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><span style=\"font-size:6.5pt;font-family:微软雅黑;color:#323232;\">（三）注意事项。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:6.5pt;font-family:微软雅黑;color:#323232;\">1.</span><span style=\"font-size:6.5pt;font-family:微软雅黑;color:#323232;\">领取准考证时间：</span><span style=\"font-size:6.5pt;font-family:微软雅黑;color:#323232;\">9</span><span style=\"font-size:6.5pt;font-family:微软雅黑;color:#323232;\">月</span><span style=\"font-size:6.5pt;font-family:微软雅黑;color:#323232;\">5</span><span style=\"font-size:6.5pt;font-family:微软雅黑;color:#323232;\">日</span><span style=\"font-size:6.5pt;font-family:微软雅黑;color:#323232;\">8</span><span style=\"font-size:6.5pt;font-family:微软雅黑;color:#323232;\">时后考生可登陆广西高等学校师资培训中心网站自行下载并打印准考证，考生也可以在考试前一天（</span><span style=\"font-size:6.5pt;font-family:微软雅黑;color:#323232;\">9</span><span style=\"font-size:6.5pt;font-family:微软雅黑;color:#323232;\">月</span><span style=\"font-size:6.5pt;font-family:微软雅黑;color:#323232;\">11</span><span style=\"font-size:6.5pt;font-family:微软雅黑;color:#323232;\">日）凭身份证、报名卡到考点领取准考证。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:6.5pt;font-family:微软雅黑;color:#323232;\">2.</span><span style=\"font-size:6.5pt;font-family:微软雅黑;color:#323232;\">考试时，考生须持准考证和身份证进入考场。如本人身份证丢失，须持当地公安机关出具的身份证明方能参考。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:6.5pt;font-family:微软雅黑;color:#323232;\">3.</span><span style=\"font-size:6.5pt;font-family:微软雅黑;color:#323232;\">考试工作由我院统一领导，广西师范大学负责做好相关考务工作。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:6.5pt;font-family:微软雅黑;color:#323232;\">五、考试收费标准</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:6.5pt;font-family:微软雅黑;color:#323232;\">报考费按照广西壮族自治区物价局、财政厅印发的桂价费函〔</span><span style=\"font-size:6.5pt;font-family:微软雅黑;color:#323232;\">2013</span><span style=\"font-size:6.5pt;font-family:微软雅黑;color:#323232;\">〕</span><span style=\"font-size:6.5pt;font-family:微软雅黑;color:#323232;\">182</span><span style=\"font-size:6.5pt;font-family:微软雅黑;color:#323232;\">号文件规定标准执行，报考费为</span><span style=\"font-size:6.5pt;font-family:微软雅